<div>Aleln&ouml;k: Becsei Andr&aacute;s, Vez&eacute;rigazgat&oacute;, OTP Jelz&aacute;logbank</div>

<div>Eln&ouml;ks&eacute;gi tagok:</div>

<div>- Heged&uuml;s &Eacute;va, Eln&ouml;k-vez&eacute;rigazgat&oacute;, Gr&aacute;nit Bank (kisbanki eln&ouml;ks&eacute;gi tagi poz&iacute;ci&oacute;ban)</div>

<div>- B&uacute;za &Eacute;va, Vez&eacute;rigazgat&oacute;, Garantiqa, Hitelgarancia,</div>

<div>- Sim&aacute;k P&aacute;l, Eln&ouml;k-vez&eacute;rigazgat&oacute;, CIB Bank,&nbsp;</div>

